htaking but heartbreaking to see how even acknowledging victims is now considered triggering for many on the left.", "last_comment_created": 1775077231549, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 11, "score_up": 264, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZ8P8m5j", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 49, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8529053, "raw_content": "I was on hold for a long enough time to go to the post office. drive back home and began cleaning up the yard. The contractor chose to hire illegals rather than pay a man what he is worth....finally spoke to the agent who answered the phone and took my information. He laughed when I shared what inspired me to call. He took down the information and the name of the construction company. He explained they are looking for the worst of the worse. the case will be sent for investigation and to not expect things to happen today...but it will be taken care of..he appreciated the call...and I appreciated all he does to help make our country safe again.", "author": "Toobigtorig1234", "created": 1775075938438, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Waffle_Stomp", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "NJ Governor strong anti Trump stance inspired me today to call ICE on illegals working a construction site... ", "last_comment_created": 1775094675325, "content": "<p>I was 